/*=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
Bluetooth State Values:
  BT_OFF = 0,
  BT_NOTCONNECTED,
  BT_CONNECTED,

Bluetooth States:

                                  BT_OFF (Using WiFi)
                                    |   ^
                      Use Bluetooth |   | Use WiFi
                     bluetoothStart |   | bluetoothStop
                                    v   |
                               BT_NOTCONNECTED
                                    |   ^
                   Client connected |   | Client disconnected
                                    v   |
                                BT_CONNECTED

=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=*/

